---------------------------------------
- Summary
---------------------------------------

Athena-Core is the base module of the Athena Game Framework, in the form
of a library written in C++.

The classes contained in that module are used by nearly all the other modules.


---------------------------------------
- Credits
---------------------------------------

Some classes of this module are based on the corresponding classes of OGRE 1.7
(Object-Oriented Graphics Rendering Engine), a scene-oriented and flexible 3D
engine, released under the MIT License. OGRE is the 3D engine used by the Athena
Game Framework.

The license of OGRE is contained in the file 'docs/LICENSE-OGRE'. 


